You're also, I think you produced this sock.

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:07.879
But the tidyverse is a collection of R tools to make data science easy and delightful in R.

00:01:09.559 --> 00:01:14.919
So I was hoping we could talk a little bit through the history. And maybe to start out,

00:01:14.919 --> 00:01:21.080
we could just go back to the very beginning, which is your very first data analysis.

00:01:22.839 --> 00:01:28.599
So it would have been at the University of Auckland where I did my undergraduate in statistics.

